Nintendo shares fall on stronger yen . Shares of Nintendo Co Ltd , a major game machine and software maker , fell sharply on Monday , hurt by the yen ' s rally against the dollar , traders said . By 0511 GMT , the share price had lost 440 yen to 8 , 910 yen on the Osaka Securities Exchange ( OSE ) . It briefly slipped as low as 8 , 850 yen . Turnover was 414 , 500 shares . While other export - oriented firms , which had also been hit by the stronger yen , recouped part of their losses on bargain - hunting , buyers were taking a wait - and - see stance on Nintendo ' s shares ahead of its earnings report due out on Tuesday . 
